{"tid":695904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭女模賣淫　「老漢推車」中遭警破門","createTime":"2018-06-09T15:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T13:28:03.000Z","uid":29627,"like":212,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"9d67539180b9df045292286fbf4a7cd1e4f11e71","tid":695904,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭女模賣淫　「老漢推車」中遭警破門<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tI2xbtsLhtE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtI2xbtsLhtE&d=b%2Ffxt4OyK%2BthaaWfjp1nWF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8b7dd919\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tI2xbtsLhtE</a><br />\n烏克蘭籍女模薇塔莉(Виталия Галлямова)，曾登上烏克蘭版花花公子(PlayBoy)版面，不過他為了生計跑到俄羅斯賣淫，遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯《life》報導，薇塔莉目前單身，獨自扶養兩個小孩，常常將生活照分享到社群網站，不過她近來苦於生計，於是決定到俄羅斯賣淫，1小時收費20萬盧布(約9萬5新台幣)，警方日前闖入飯店內，逮到薇塔莉跟客戶正在進行性交易，起初她堅決否認，但警方拿出拍攝的影片後，她便改口坦承犯行。薇塔莉除了面臨罰款後，還可能被俄羅斯驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180609/640_c074819cb69285832e3759895dd2185f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180609%2F640_c074819cb69285832e3759895dd2185f.jpg&h=24e21662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180609/640_8eddcc423bd9b1ff80e37758193d87ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180609%2F640_8eddcc423bd9b1ff80e37758193d87ae.jpg&h=30379092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180609/640_ca8662eeb892c1181787a6a837ba70b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180609%2F640_ca8662eeb892c1181787a6a837ba70b9.jpg&h=64b44853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180609/640_549761290aa6037d341bbaabfbd83498.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.